[src:generating-functions/exponential-generating-function-p02] Generating functions give us several methods to manipulate sums and to establish identities between sums.
[src:generating-functions/exponential-generating-function-p02] The simplest case occurs when *sn* = Σ*n* *k* = 0 *ak*.
